### Регистрация нового пользователя для теста
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testpassword@example.com",
  "password": "oldpassword123",
  "nameFirst": "Test",
  "nameLast": "Password"
}

### Логин для получения токена
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testpassword@example.com",
  "password": "oldpassword123"
}

### Смена пароля (замените YOUR_JWT_TOKEN на токен из логина)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/change-password
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

{
  "oldPassword": "oldpassword123",
  "newPassword": "newpassword456"
}

### Проверка нового пароля - логин с новым паролем
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testpassword@example.com",
  "password": "newpassword456"
}

### Проверка старого пароля - должен вернуть ошибку
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testpassword@example.com",
  "password": "oldpassword123"
}
